firepy - a git clone of the python based firephp implementation
===============================================================

original page: http://code.google.com/p/firepy/
original svn source: http://firepy.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/

Documentation
-------------

best to read the original documentation:
http://code.google.com/p/firepy/wiki/Documentation

Installation
------------

* install the FirePHP Plugin for Firebug: http://www.firephp.org/
* integrate firepy in your django project